---
const today = new Date();
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<footer class="bg-earth-100 border-t border-earth-200">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <!-- Logo and description -->
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 mr-2 text-olive-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-xl font-bold text-earth-900">{SITE_TITLE}</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-earth-700 mb-4">Explorando as profundezas da sabedoria clássica e do pensamento filosófico no mundo moderno. Junte-se a nós em uma jornada pelas ideias antigas que permanecem profundamente relevantes hoje.</p>
        <div class="flex space-x-4 text-earth-700">
          <a href="https://scholar.google.com" target="_blank" class="hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">
            <span class="sr-only">Google Scholar</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M5.242 13.769L0 9.5 12 0l12 9.5-5.242 4.269C17.548 11.249 14.978 9.5 12 9.5c-2.977 0-5.548 1.748-6.758 4.269zM12 10a7 7 0 1 0 0 14 7 7 0 0 0 0-14z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" class="hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">
            <span class="sr-only">Twitter</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M24 4.557c-.883.392-1.832.656-2.828.775 1.017-.609 1.798-1.574 2.165-2.724-.951.564-2.005.974-3.127 1.195-.897-.957-2.178-1.555-3.594-1.555-3.179 0-5.515 2.966-4.797 6.045-4.091-.205-7.719-2.165-10.148-5.144-1.29 2.213-.669 5.108 1.523 6.574-.806-.026-1.566-.247-2.229-.616-.054 2.281 1.581 4.415 3.949 4.89-.693.188-1.452.232-2.224.084.626 1.956 2.444 3.379 4.6 3.419-2.07 1.623-4.678 2.348-7.29 2.04 2.179 1.397 4.768 2.212 7.548 2.212 9.142 0 14.307-7.721 13.995-14.646.962-.695 1.797-1.562 2.457-2.549z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">
            <span class="sr-only">GitHub</span>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Links column 1 -->
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-earth-900 mb-4">Explore</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">Blog</a></li>
          <li><a href="/categories" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">Categories</a></li>
          <li><a href="/courses" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">Courses</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">About</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Links column 2 -->
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-earth-900 mb-4">Key Topics</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/categories/philosophy" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">Philosophy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/categories/classics" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">Classical Studies</a></li>
          <li><a href="/categories/literature" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">Ancient Literature</a></li>
          <li><a href="/categories/history" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">Ancient History</a></li>
          <li><a href="/categories/mythology" class="text-earth-700 hover:text-olive-600 transition duration-200">Mythology</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-earth-200 text-center text-earth-600">
      <p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} {SITE_TITLE}. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Dedicated to the preservation and study of classical wisdom.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
